Do NOT use: generic ML observations that work for any AI company ("the hardest part of AI is production", "inference is the bottleneck everywhere", etc.)

== PARAGRAPH 1 — What {{ company }} is doing and why it matters (3–4 sentences) ==
Explain what {{ company }} is specifically working on and what makes it interesting or important.
